<h2 style="text-align: center;">Information and Time</h2>
<p>Gisin, 67, is primarily an experimenter. He runs a lab at the University of Geneva that has performed groundbreaking experiments in quantum communication and quantum cryptography. But he is also the rare crossover physicist who is known for important theoretical insights, especially ones involving quantum chance and nonlocality.</p>
<p>On Sunday mornings, in lieu of church, Gisin makes a habit of sitting quietly in his chair at home with a mug of oolong tea and contemplating deep conceptual puzzles. It was on a Sunday about two and a half years ago that he realized that the deterministic picture of time in Einstein’s theory and the rest of “classical” physics implicitly assumes the existence of infinite information.</p>
<div id='component-5e9e42be5ca32'><script type="text/template">{"type":"Image","id":"component-5e9e42be5ca32","data":{"id":84263,"src":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg","class":"","width":2000,"height":2000,"mobileSrc":false,"zoomSrc":false,"align":"align=\"right\"","wrapper_width":"","caption":"<p>Nicolas Gisin in his home office overlooking the garden.<\/p>\n","attribution":"<p>Carole Parodi<\/p>\n","variant":"shortcode","size":"wide","disableZoom":true,"srcImage":{"ID":84263,"id":84263,"title":"Gisin-Parodi_2000","filename":"Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg","filesize":1433835,"url":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg","link":"https:\/\/www.quantamagazine.org\/does-time-really-flow-new-clues-come-from-a-century-old-approach-to-math-20200407\/gisin-parodi_2000\/","alt":"Nicolas Gisin portrait.","author":"13691","description":"Carole Parodi","caption":"Nicolas Gisin in his home office overlooking the garden.\n","name":"gisin-parodi_2000","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":84064,"date":"2020-04-06 21:05:40","modified":"2020-04-07 12:59:04","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image\/jpeg","type":"image","subtype":"jpeg","icon":"https:\/\/api.quantamagazine.org\/wp-includes\/images\/media\/default.png","width":2000,"height":2000,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-520x520.jpg","thumbnail-width":520,"thumbnail-height":520,"medium":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1720x1720.jpg","medium-width":1720,"medium-height":1720,"medium_large":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-768x768.jpg","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":768,"large":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg","large-width":2000,"large-height":2000,"square_small":"https:\/\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Gisin-Paro