g quietly in his chair at home with a mug of oolong tea and contemplating deep conceptual puzzles. It was on a Sunday about two and a half years ago that he realized that the deterministic picture of time in Einstein’s theory and the rest of “classical” physics implicitly assumes the existence of infinite information.\u003c/p>\n\u003cdiv id='component-5e9e42be5ca32'>\u003cscript type=\"text/template\">{\"type\":\"Image\",\"id\":\"component-5e9e42be5ca32\",\"data\":{\"id\":84263,\"src\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg\",\"class\":\"\",\"width\":2000,\"height\":2000,\"mobileSrc\":false,\"zoomSrc\":false,\"align\":\"align=\\\"right\\\"\",\"wrapper_width\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\u003cp>Nicolas Gisin in his home office overlooking the garden.\u003c\\/p>\\n\",\"attribution\":\"\u003cp>Carole Parodi\u003c\\/p>\\n\",\"variant\":\"shortcode\",\"size\":\"wide\",\"disableZoom\":true,\"srcImage\":{\"ID\":84263,\"id\":84263,\"title\":\"Gisin-Parodi_2000\",\"filename\":\"Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg\",\"filesize\":1433835,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg\",\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.quantamagazine.org\\/does-time-really-flow-new-clues-come-from-a-century-old-approach-to-math-20200407\\/gisin-parodi_2000\\/\",\"alt\":\"Nicolas Gisin portrait.\",\"author\":\"13691\",\"description\":\"Carole Parodi\",\"caption\":\"Nicolas Gisin in his home office overlooking the garden.\\n\",\"name\":\"gisin-parodi_2000\",\"status\":\"inherit\",\"uploaded_to\":84064,\"date\":\"2020-04-06 21:05:40\",\"modified\":\"2020-04-07 12:59:04\",\"menu_order\":0,\"mime_type\":\"image\\/jpeg\",\"type\":\"image\",\"subtype\":\"jpeg\",\"icon\":\"https:\\/\\/api.quantamagazine.org\\/wp-includes\\/images\\/media\\/default.png\",\"width\":2000,\"height\":2000,\"sizes\":{\"thumbnail\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-520x520.jpg\",\"thumbnail-width\":520,\"thumbnail-height\":520,\"medium\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1720x1720.jpg\",\"medium-width\":1720,\"medium-height\":1720,\"medium_large\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-768x768.jpg\",\"medium_large-width\":768,\"medium_large-height\":768,\"large\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000.jpg\",\"large-width\":2000,\"large-height\":2000,\"square_small\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-160x160.jpg\",\"square_small-width\":160,\"square_small-height\":160,\"square_large\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-520x520.jpg\",\"square_large-width\":520,\"square_large-height\":520,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_12_9\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1832x1374.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_landscape_12_9-width\":1832,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_12_9-height\":1374,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_9_7\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1376x1032.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_landscape_9_7-width\":1376,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_9_7-height\":1032,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_5_5\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1044x783.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_landscape_5_5-width\":1044,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_5_5-height\":783,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_4_7\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-632x474.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_landscape_4_7-width\":632,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_4_7-height\":474,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_4_0\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-536x402.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_landscape_4_0-width\":536,\"apple_news_ca_landscape_4_0-height\":402,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_12_9\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1122x1496.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_portrait_12_9-width\":1122,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_12_9-height\":1496,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_9_7\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-840x1120.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_portrait_9_7-width\":840,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_9_7-height\":1120,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_5_5\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-687x916.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_portrait_5_5-width\":687,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_5_5-height\":916,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_4_7\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-414x552.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_portrait_4_7-width\":414,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_4_7-height\":552,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_4_0\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-354x472.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_portrait_4_0-width\":354,\"apple_news_ca_portrait_4_0-height\":472,\"apple_news_ca_square_12_9\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1472x1472.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_square_12_9-width\":1472,\"apple_news_ca_square_12_9-height\":1472,\"apple_news_ca_square_9_7\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-1104x1104.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_square_9_7-width\":1104,\"apple_news_ca_square_9_7-height\":1104,\"apple_news_ca_square_5_5\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-912x912.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_square_5_5-width\":912,\"apple_news_ca_square_5_5-height\":912,\"apple_news_ca_square_4_7\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-550x550.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_square_4_7-width\":550,\"apple_news_ca_square_4_7-height\":550,\"apple_news_ca_square_4_0\":\"https:\\/\\/d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net\\/uploads\\/2020\\/04\\/Gisin-Parodi_2000-470x470.jpg\",\"apple_news_ca_square_4_0-width\":470,\"apple_news_ca_square_4_0-height\":470}},\"largeForPrint\":false,\"externalLink\":\"\"}}\u003c\/script>\u003c/div>\n\u003cp>Consider the weather. Because it’s chaotic, or highly sensitive to small differences, we can’t predict exactly what the weather will be a week from now. But because it’s a classical system, textbooks tell us that we could, in principle, predict the weather a week on, if only we could measure every cloud, gust of wind and butterfly’s wing precisely enough. It’s our own fault we can’t gauge conditions with enough decimal digits of detail to extrapolate forward and make perfectly accurate forecasts, because the actual physics of weather unfolds like clockwork.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>Now expand this idea to the entire universe. In a predetermined world in which time only seems to unfold, exactly what will happen for all time actually had to be set from the start, with the initial state of every single particle encoded with infinitely many digits of precision. Otherwise there would be a time in the far future when the clockwork universe itself would break down.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>But information is physical. Modern research shows it requires energy and occupies space. Any volume of space is known to have a finite information capacity (with the densest possible information storage happening inside black holes). The universe’s initial conditions would, Gisin realized, require far too much information crammed into too little space. “A real number with infinite digits can’t be physically relevant,” he said. The block universe, which implicitly assumes the existence of infinite information, must fall apart.\u003c/p>\n\u003cp>He sought a new way of describing time in physics that didn’t presume infinitely precise knowledge of the initial conditions.\u003c/p>\n\u003cdiv id='component-5e9e42be605ba'>\u003cscript type=\"text/template\">{\"type\":\"Image\",\"id\":\"component-5e9e42be605ba\",\"data\":{\"id\":84303,\"src\":\"https:\\